songs.title: The Tide (밀물) [Scratch by DJ Friz]
songs.lyrics:
Wigie cheohan geudae
Da tteomillyeoganeunde
Mulgyeore jeohangeul hae
Sesangeun eohanginge

Eoneudeot seumurinde
Nakksibaneureul pihae
Andoui sumeul swine
Sesangeun geumurinde

Swim, swim, swim away
Nae kkumi geudae aneseo Dive ik sahae
Swim, swim, swim away
Nae salmi geudae aneseo Dive ik sahae

Modeun seoneul garochae
Bandeuthameul gangyohae
Jikseoni dwirago hwieojin jaro jae
Dallirago hae
Sanbangi byeokinde
Byeokdoreul eonjimyeonseo deungeul tteomine
Neon byeorinde
Eoreundeurui heotdwin sowon ttaemune byeolttongbyeori dwae
Neo ege sabeul geonnejun soni songarakjil hae
Seuseuro mudeom pan georae

Swim, swim, swim away
Nae kkumi geudae aneseo Dive ik sahae
Swim, swim, swim away
Nae salmi geudae aneseo Dive ik sahae

Wigie cheoham geudae
Da tteomillyeoganeunde
Mulgyeore jeohangeul hae
Sesangeun eohanginde

Eoneudeot seumurinde
Nakksibaneureul pihae
Andoui sumeul swine
Sesangeun geumurinde

Wigie cheoham geudae
Da tteomillyeoganeunde
Mulgyeore jeohangeul hae
Sesangeun eohanginde

Eoneudeot seumurinde
Nakksibaneureul pihae
Andoui sumeul swine
Sesangeun geumurinde

Swim, swim, swim away
Nae kkumi geudae aneseo Dive ik sahae
Swim, swim, swim away
Nae salmi geudae aneseo Dive ik sahae

Ik sahae
